{
  "stem": "18258.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in 1921, it was a little bit difficult time of [? reinteresting. ?] But in 1916, something else happened interesting.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember one afternoon, I walked proudly along in front of the store, and I had a little rucksack with a slate board and a little sponge, and the little ink.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was ready for first grade.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I hoped everybody of the passengers saw me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "After all, I was going to school the next day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that day started something which was very influential in my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That very first day, I found out that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What happened in Austria-- religious instruction was mandatory in schools up to age 18.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I believe it still is now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But at that time-- the first grade-- the teacher told the whole class-- I think there were about 40 to 45 boys-- that the priest would come twice a week and instruct our boys in the catechism, the Christian Bible.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then she said, of course, I know there are some of you are Protestants and some are Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You will have to-- well, she didn't say Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was not genteel enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She called us Israelites.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you will have to go twice a week in the afternoon, after regular school hours, to a centralized district school where there would be a minister of the Protestants or a Jewish-- maybe a rabbi, or anyway, an instructor to instruct you in your religion.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then she asked, who are the Protestants?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were three boys who raised their hands.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two were Lutherans, and was-- one was a Calvinist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to go to different schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now where are the Israelites?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No-- I had no idea what an Israelite was.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
